CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780521072
OL,3,CTwo warriors reunited two decades
OL,4,Clater after two astounding acts of
OL,5,Cbravery
OL,7,FJust 23 years old when he was sent to
OL,8,FIraq, Private Johnson, as he was then,
OL,9,Fearned the Victoria Cross for two
OL,10,Fseparate acts of bravery under enemy
OL,11,Ffire.
OL,13,FThat was 22 years ago. Today, he was
OL,14,Freunited with the Warrior, which has
OL,15,Fjust been decommissioned after 40
OL,16,Fyears of service, most recently
OL,17,Fdeploying to Estonia as part of a Nato
OL,18,Foperation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780521072
OL,3,CTwo warriors reunited two decades
OL,4,Clater after two astounding acts of
OL,5,Cbravery
OL,7,FThe pair were reintroduced outside the
OL,8,FNational Army Museum in London, where
OL,9,Fthe Warrior is currently on free
OL,10,Fdisplay outside.
OL,12,F"It's giving me goosebumps" said
OL,13,FBeharry, checking its underside for
OL,14,Fsigns of the damage inflicted by RPG's
OL,15,Fand landmines encountered while he was
OL,16,Fat the wheel.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
