PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780521072
OL,3,CTwo warriors reunited two decades
OL,4,Clater after two astounding acts of
OL,5,Cbravery
OL,7,FBeharry was the first living British
OL,8,Fsoldier in 35 years to be awarded the
OL,9,FVictoria Cross after saving the lives
OL,10,Fof his comrades during ambushes in
OL,11,FIraq.
OL,13,FOn May 1, 2004, after his platoon
OL,14,Fcommander was wounded in an attack,
OL,15,FBeharry took control of the Warrior
OL,16,Fvehicle.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
