PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780521072
OL,3,CTwo warriors reunited two decades
OL,4,Clater after two astounding acts of
OL,5,Cbravery
OL,7,FDespite being severely injured, he
OL,8,Fmanaged to escape from the burning
OL,9,Fvehicle and carried his wounded
OL,10,Fcolleagues to safety, all while under
OL,11,Fheavy machine-gun fire.
OL,13,F"I ran through the fire" he said. "I
OL,14,Fwas like 'Boss are you ok?' I didn't
OL,15,Fget any response from him, so I
OL,16,Fgrabbed his helmet ... I pulled him
OL,17,Fup, I put him on my back and I carried
OL,18,Fhim through the fire into the next
OL,19,Fvehicle"
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@XO]uD@cOU{D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
