PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780521072
OL,3,CTwo warriors reunited two decades
OL,4,Clater after two astounding acts of
OL,5,Cbravery
OL,7,FHe went back three times for his
OL,8,Fremaining crew members.
OL,10,FIn a second ambush a month later,
OL,11,FBeharry sustained a severe head injury
OL,12,Ffrom a rocket-propelled grenade but
OL,13,Fstill drove his vehicle out of danger,
OL,14,Fsaving the lives of those around him
OL,15,Fbefore losing consciousness.
OL,17,FThe museum is also displaying
OL,18,FBeharry's Victoria Cross, alongside
OL,19,Fthe helmet he was wearing, both on
OL,20,Floan from Lord Ashcroft's collection.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
