PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780521072
OL,3,CTwo warriors reunited two decades
OL,4,Clater after two astounding acts of
OL,5,Cbravery
OL,7,FBut having barely escaped with his
OL,8,Flife from the second attack, Beharry
OL,9,Fhas no recollection of it.
OL,11,F"I wish the Warrior could speak" he
OL,12,Fsaid, his hand on its headlamp. "I
OL,13,Fcan't remember ... only it knows what
OL,14,Fwe've been through together".
